{
  "stem": "2723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the separation moment became necessary, my mother and aunt disappeared into the vaults of the bank with some other people that the bank wanted to-- it was very much like Anne Frank, really.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister and I were taken, at night, to the janitor's house, where we were literally put, during the day, under the [NON-ENGLISH], into their bed, which housed all their smells and all their personal life, I guess.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were covered with a [NON-ENGLISH], with an airlock, and had to lie still the whole day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I guess it was a great test for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could only play word games and often got on each other's nerves to a point of despair.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What sustained us was our mother's contact by letter, which she sent to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I do have a letter of hers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I am unable to talk about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's too painful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were fed well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At night, we were let out of the bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we could use the outside toilet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was getting cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We could read books during the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we-- our body clock completely became haywire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we turned around and we hated being there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We really did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Although they were very, very decent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I would like to call them righteous gentiles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it must have been about three weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But time has so little meaning, looking back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because part of that time we were also in the laundry of this-- the building where the Germans were hidden, in a crate.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he became afraid-- his name was Gustav.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
